    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term for several species of short-horned grasshoppers that become gregarious, migratory, and increase greatly in numbers under suitable conditions, forming destructive swarms that can travel great distances, rapidly damaging crops and stripping fields.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
